---
// components/Footer.astro
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="text-footer-light py-10 text-sm bg-secondary">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-18 py-12">
    <!-- Top Section -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-between gap-10">
      <!-- Logo & Description -->
      <div class="flex-1 max-w-md">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <!-- <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Totalis Logo" class="h-10 w-auto" /> -->
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold">TOTALIS</div>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-2">
          Totalis – Doors and Windows by Hindalco, are crafted from eternally
          recyclable aluminium and undergo rigorous testing against wind load,
          water penetration, and air infiltration.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-2">
          This commitment to testing ensures that customers can place their
          trust in the durability and reliability of Totalis products.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="underline hover:text-primary">Read More</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="hover:text-primary">About us</a>
          <a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary">Services</a>
          <a href="/products" class="hover:text-primary">Products</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-primary">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary">Linkedin</a>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary">Twitter</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
          <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-primary">Terms and Conditions</a>
          <!-- <span>Copyright © 2023</span> -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider & Legal -->
    <div
      class="border-t border-white/20 pt-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4 text-xs"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-primary">Terms of Use</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-primary">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/cookies" class="hover:text-primary">About Cookies</a>
      </div>
      <div>&copy; {currentYear} Totalis by HINDALCO. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Final Note -->
    <div class="text-xs text-footer-light/80">
      Totalis Business empowers organizations with comprehensive tools for
      financial transparency, offering intuitive features for budgeting, expense
      tracking, financial reporting, and analytics—so businesses can clearly
      understand and communicate their financial health.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
